000\"><span style=\"font-weight:700\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">B.D. / B.Def / Basse-d&eacute;f</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top:19px; margin-bottom:19px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.2\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-65e1d3e3-7fff-2f0a-a96d-ebbf26f145db\" style=\"font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">Basse&nbsp;D&eacute;finition. Tout visuel dont la r&eacute;solution est inf&eacute;rieure &agrave; 300&nbsp;DPI.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top:19px; margin-bottom:19px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top:19px; margin-bottom:19px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.2\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-65e1d3e3-7fff-2f0a-a96d-ebbf26f145db\" style=\"font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:700\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">Blind&#39;ej</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top:19px; margin-bottom:19px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.2\"><b style=\"font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">Un BLIND&#39;EJ, k&eacute;sako ?<br />\r\nUne fois par mois, sur les sites de Paris et de Lyon/Tournon.&nbsp;<br />\r\nToujours le 1er mardi du mois (pas comme un certain programme &agrave; la t&eacute;l&eacute; 😏)<br />\r\nUn resto offert par Insign, &agrave; 10 minutes &agrave; pied maximum du bureau (pas d&rsquo;excuse pour les feignants)<br />\r\n6 personnes de n&rsquo;importe quelle entit&eacute;, cellule ou grade hi&eacute;rarchique (m&ecirc;me si chez nous, on pense plut&ocirc;t &agrave; l&rsquo;horizontal qu&rsquo;&agrave; la verticale)<br />\r\nL&rsquo;identit&eacute; de tes compagnons de d&eacute;jeuner gard&eacute;e secr&egrave;te jusqu&rsquo;au dernier moment<br />\r\nUne invitation Google Agenda envoy&eacute;e &agrave; l&rsquo;avance indiquant le jour et l&rsquo;heure &agrave; laquelle il suffira de r&eacute;pondre, tout le reste sera g&eacute;r&eacute; par la merveilleuse &eacute;quipe organisatrice des BLIND&#39;EJS</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top:19px; margin-bottom:19px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top:19px; margin-bottom:19px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.2\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-65e1d3e3-7fff-2f0a-a96d-ebbf26f145db\" style=\"font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:700\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">Brand Content</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top:19px; margin-bottom:19px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.2\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-65e1d3e3-7fff-2f0a-a96d-ebbf26f145db\" style=\"font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">Dans l&rsquo;absolu, tout contenu original cr&eacute;&eacute; pour une marque. En Production, employ&eacute; essentiellement pour parler de mini-films cr&eacute;&eacute;s sp&eacute;cifiquement pour le web ou les r&eacute;seaux sociaux.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top:19px; margin-bottom:19px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.2\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-65e1d3e3-7fff-2f0a-a96d-ebbf26f145db\" style=\"font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:700\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">B.T.L.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top:19px; margin-bottom:19px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.2\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-65e1d3e3-7fff-2f0a-a96d-ebbf26f145db\" style=\"font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">Below The Line. Ce qui n&rsquo;a pas trait directement aux budgets publicitaires, et par extension les livrables associ&eac