00\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">Kivi / K.V.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top:19px; margin-bottom:19px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.2\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-65e1d3e3-7fff-2f0a-a96d-ebbf26f145db\" style=\"font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">Key Visual. Visuel principal d&rsquo;une campagne, qui fera r&eacute;f&eacute;rence pour toutes les d&eacute;clinaisons visuelles.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top:19px; margin-bottom:19px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.2\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-65e1d3e3-7fff-2f0a-a96d-ebbf26f145db\" style=\"font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:700\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">Maquette</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top:19px; margin-bottom:19px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.2\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-65e1d3e3-7fff-2f0a-a96d-ebbf26f145db\" style=\"font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">Maquette visuelle d&rsquo;une affiche ou d&rsquo;une annonce, mais aussi aper&ccedil;u mont&eacute; d&rsquo;un objet d&rsquo;impression.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">On parle de&nbsp;maquette &eacute;cras&eacute;e&nbsp;ou&nbsp;aplatie&nbsp;pour signifier que tous les&nbsp;calques&nbsp;qui la composent ont &eacute;t&eacute; fusionn&eacute;s. Voir la d&eacute;finition des calques pour la distinction entre calques&nbsp;aplatis&nbsp;et&nbsp;s&eacute;par&eacute;s.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">Une&nbsp;maquette assembl&eacute;e&nbsp;&hellip;</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top:19px; margin-bottom:19px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.2\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-65e1d3e3-7fff-2f0a-a96d-ebbf26f145db\" style=\"font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:700\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">Parcours Consommateur / Parcours Conso&rsquo;</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top:19px; margin-bottom:19px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.2\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-65e1d3e3-7fff-2f0a-a96d-ebbf26f145db\" style=\"font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">De son nom anglais&nbsp;Consumer Journey&nbsp;ou&nbsp;Consumer Journey. Le parcours d&rsquo;un utilisateur &agrave; travers tous les points de contact avec la marque, qu&rsquo;ils soient physiques ou num&eacute;riques.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">En phase de conception, on r&eacute;fl&eacute;chit &agrave; cr&eacute;er des parcours, pour amener le consommateur d&rsquo;un point A &agrave; un point B, g&eacute;n&eacute;ralement de la premi&egrave;re exposition &agrave; un message jusqu&rsquo;&agrave; l&rsquo;acte d&rsquo;achat, &agrave; l&rsquo;inscription &agrave; un service, ou au partage du message avec un autre consommateur. Le parcours comprend donc aussi bien une affiche qu&rsquo;un site internet, une interaction en magasin qu&rsquo;un post social, une pub TV qu&rsquo;un email de relance.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top:19px; margin-bottom:19px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.2\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-65e1d3e3-7fff-2f0a-a96d-ebbf26f145db\" style=\"font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:700\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">Signat&rsquo;</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top:19px; margin-bottom:19px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.2\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-65e1d3e3-7fff-2f0a-a96d-ebbf26f145db\" style=\"font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">Signature. La phrase accompagnant le logo de marque ou de produit sur un print ou un film.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top:19px; margin-bottom:19px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.2\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-65e1d3e3-7fff-2f0a-a96d-ebbf26f145db\" style=\"font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:700\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">Story&rsquo; / Storyboard</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top:19px; margin-bottom:19px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.2\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-65e1d3e3-7fff-2f0a-a96d-ebbf26f145db\" style=\"font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">Ensemble de planches illustr&eacute;es expliquant le d&eacute;roul&eacute; d&rsquo;un film ou d&rsquo;une&nbsp;banni&egrave;re.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top:19px; margin-bottom:19px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.2\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-65e1d3e3-7fff-2f0a-a96d-ebbf26f145db\" style=\"font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:700\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">Trafic Manager</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top:19px; margin-bottom:19px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.2\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-65e1d3e3-7fff-2f0a-a96d-ebbf26f145db\" style=\"font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">En agence non m&eacute;dia, le responsable de la planification du travail cr&eacute;atif. En agence digitale, la planification s&rsquo;&eacute;tend aussi aux ressources techniques internes (voir&nbsp;d&eacute;veloppeur).