e=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">De l&rsquo;anglais&nbsp;embedded. Veut dire que le contenu dont on parle (g&eacute;n&eacute;ralement une vid&eacute;o) sera &ldquo;int&eacute;gr&eacute; &agrave; l&rsquo;int&eacute;rieur de&rdquo; : d&rsquo;une page, d&rsquo;une application, etc.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top:19px; margin-bottom:19px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.2\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-65e1d3e3-7fff-2f0a-a96d-ebbf26f145db\" style=\"font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:700\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">Expand (banner)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top:19px; margin-bottom:19px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.2\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-65e1d3e3-7fff-2f0a-a96d-ebbf26f145db\" style=\"font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">Format&nbsp;de&nbsp;banni&egrave;re&nbsp;qui se d&eacute;plie et s&#39;agrandit quand on passe la souris au-dessus.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top:19px; margin-bottom:19px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.2\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-65e1d3e3-7fff-2f0a-a96d-ebbf26f145db\" style=\"font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:700\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">Format</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top:19px; margin-bottom:19px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.2\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-65e1d3e3-7fff-2f0a-a96d-ebbf26f145db\" style=\"font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">Mot employ&eacute; pour signifier tout type de format publicitaire digital. Comprend les banni&egrave;res, les formats sp&eacute;cifiques aux r&eacute;seaux sociaux, les&nbsp;habillages, les vid&eacute;os. Plus d&rsquo;infos :&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><a href=\"https://www.veinteractive.com/fr/blog/rich-media-cinemagraph-les-formats-de-la-publicite-digitale-en-2016/\" style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#1155cc\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none\"><span style=\"text-decoration-skip-ink:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">https://www.veinteractive.com/fr/blog/rich-media-cinemagraph-les-formats-de-la-publicite-digitale-en-2016/</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></a></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top:19px; margin-bottom:19px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.2\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-65e1d3e3-7fff-2f0a-a96d-ebbf26f145db\" style=\"font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:700\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">Format Classique</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top:19px; margin-bottom:19px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.2\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-65e1d3e3-7fff-2f0a-a96d-ebbf26f145db\" style=\"font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">Format&nbsp;de&nbsp;banni&egrave;re&nbsp;simple, aux dimensions standards, et sans interactivit&eacute;, sinon le clic renvoyant vers un site de destination. Ces formats sont g&eacute;n&eacute;ralements le&nbsp;Pav&eacute;&nbsp;(300x250 pixels), le&nbsp;Carr&eacute;&nbsp;(250x250 pixels), la&nbsp;M&eacute;ga Banni&egrave;re&nbsp;(728x90 pixels), et le&nbsp;Skyscraper&nbsp;(120x600 pixels ou 160x600 pixels).</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top:19px; margin-bottom:19px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.2\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-65e1d3e3-7fff-2f0a-a96d-ebbf26f145db\" style=\"font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:700\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">GIF / GIF anim&eacute;</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top:19px; margin-bottom:19px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.2\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-65e1d3e3-7fff-2f0a-a96d-ebbf26f145db\" style=\"font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">Prononc&eacute; &ldquo;jif&rdquo;.&nbsp;Format d&rsquo;image sp&eacute;cifique au web et permettant d&rsquo;afficher du contenu anim&eacute;. Le GIF est un format simple &agrave; manipuler, mais avec de nombreuses contraintes : 256 couleurs maximum, transparence rudimentaire, et principe d&rsquo;animation par affichage successif d&rsquo;images. Ce format est plus adapt&eacute; aux images avec des grands aplats de couleurs et des formes simples.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top:19px; margin-bottom:19px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.2\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-65e1d3e3-7fff-2f0a-a96d-ebbf26f145db\" style=\"font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:700\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">Habillage</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top:19px; margin-bottom:19px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.2\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-65e1d3e3-7fff-2f0a-a96d-ebbf26f145db\" style=\"font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">Format publicitaire qui n&rsquo;est pas une banni&egrave;re mais accompagne souvent celle-ci. C&rsquo;est un d&eacute;cor de fond qui &ldquo;habille&rdquo; la page qui l&rsquo;accueille, et qui se pr&eacute;sente g&eacute;n&eacute;ralement sous la forme d&rsquo;un U ou d&rsquo;un L invers&eacute;s.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top:19px; margin-bottom:19px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.2\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-65e1d3e3-7fff-2f0a-a96d-ebbf26f145db\" style=\"font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">Exemple d&rsquo;habillage : publicit&eacute; pour Bienvenue chez les Ch&rsquo;tis sur le site Allocin&eacute;.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top:19px; margin-bottom:19px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.2\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-65e1d3e3-7fff-2f0a-a96d-ebbf26f145db\" style=\"font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:700\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">I.A.B. / Pack I.A.B.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top:19px; margin-bottom:19px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.2\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-65e1d3e3-7fff-2f0a-a96d-ebbf26f145db\" style=\"font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">International Advertising Bureau. L&rsquo;organisme international charg&eacute; de standardiser tous les formats publicitaires digitaux.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">Un&nbsp;Pack IAB, ou &ldquo;un IAB&rdquo;, est g&eacute;n&eacute;ralement compris comme l&rsquo;ensemble des 3 formats les plus courants d&rsquo;une campagne digitale : le&nbsp;rectangle&nbsp;ou&nbsp;carr&eacute;, la&nbsp;m&eacute;ga banni&egrave;re, et le&nbsp;skyscraper.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top:19px; margin-bottom:19px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.2\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-65e1d3e3-7fff-2f0a-a96d-ebbf26f145db\" style=\"font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:700\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">In-feed</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top:19px; margin-bottom:19px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.2\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-65e1d3e3-7fff-2f0a-a96d-ebbf26f145db\" style=\"font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">Les formats&nbsp;in-feed&nbsp;ont pour particularit&eacute; de se trouver au sein m&ecirc;me du flux d&rsquo;informations du site. Ils reprennent l&rsquo;apparence et l&rsquo;ergonomie de leur environnement &eacute;ditorial.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">Exemple : un&nbsp;native ad&nbsp;ou un format&nbsp;display&nbsp;au milieu d&rsquo;un article.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top:19px; margin-bottom:19px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.2\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-65e1d3e3-7fff-2f0a-a96d-ebbf26f145db\" style=\"font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span s