an style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">Prononc&eacute; &ldquo;Jipeg&rdquo;. Format d&rsquo;image issu du web. G&egrave;re 16,7 millions de couleurs mais pas la transparence. Plus adapt&eacute; aux images photographiques. Ce format permet de g&eacute;n&eacute;rer des images relativement l&eacute;g&egrave;res gr&acirc;ce &agrave; une compression importante, mais la qualit&eacute; de rendu en est facilement d&eacute;grad&eacute;e. Il ne permet pas les animations.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top:19px; margin-bottom:19px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.2\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-65e1d3e3-7fff-2f0a-a96d-ebbf26f145db\" style=\"font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:18pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:700\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">Landing Page / Landing</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-top:19px; margin-bottom:19px\"><span style=\"line-height:1.2\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-65e1d3e3-7fff-2f0a-a96d-ebbf26f145db\" style=\"font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\">Page de site web servant de (premi&egrave;re) destination pour l&rsquo;utilisateur ayant cliqu&eacute; sur une&nbsp;banni&egrave;re, un lien partag&eacute;